<div class="title">Heart Rate Shot Up</div>
<div class="substance">Cannabis, Amphetamines (Adderall) & Salvia divinorum</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=LrgSmplDgrm&Exact=1">LrgSmplDgrm</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; LrgSmplDgrm. "Heart Rate Shot Up: An Experience with Cannabis, Amphetamines (Adderall) & Salvia divinorum (exp11232)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 14, 2005. erowid.org/exp/11232</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
